{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "name": "Setup",
  "slug": "soc-setup",
  "description": "One-time and ongoing admin configuration.",
  "tags": [
    "socmetric"
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "099fb995346f31c7",
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": null,
      "body": "**SOCMetric** \u00b7 Last sync: `<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.last_sync_completed_at | relative_time>>` \u00b7 Status: `<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.last_sync_status>>`"
    },
    {
      "id": "d72e5ee9b3678339",
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": null,
      "body": "| [Home](/pages/soc-dashboard-home) | [Calendar](/pages/soc-calendar) | [Watch Status](/pages/soc-watch-status) | [Flow](/pages/soc-flow) | [Response Speed](/pages/soc-response-speed) | [Capacity](/pages/soc-capacity) | [Patterns](/pages/soc-patterns) | [Projections](/pages/soc-projections) | [Context Ledger](/pages/soc-context-ledger) | [Setup](/pages/soc-setup) |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "63d721d24d2dde77",
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": null,
      "visibility_formula": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.first_sync_completed_at == null>>",
      "body": "> Setup is incomplete. Open the [Setup page](/pages/soc-setup) to configure the project, classify statuses, and run the first sync."
    },
    {
      "id": "8ddf878039b70767",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Status"
    },
    {
      "id": "fac989447cad2edb",
      "type": "metric_card",
      "title": "Project",
      "value_formula": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.project_key | default('(not set)')>>"
    },
    {
      "id": "c0828e0381730bef",
      "type": "metric_card",
      "title": "Sync status",
      "value_formula": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.last_sync_status>>"
    },
    {
      "id": "7e7cb6814b74d659",
      "type": "metric_card",
      "title": "First sync",
      "value_formula": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.first_sync_completed_at | relative_time | default('never')>>"
    },
    {
      "id": "437f57809f82b9e2",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Project selection"
    },
    {
      "id": "425db905039f7a65",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Discover projects",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "discover_projects"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9d7115b42254d59b",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "label": "Project",
      "options_formula": "<<STORY_RESULT('soc_data').projects>>",
      "option_label_field": "name",
      "option_value_field": "key",
      "bind_to": "selected_project"
    },
    {
      "id": "3e8d88fdd85d7153",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Save project",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "settings_op",
          "op": "set",
          "key": "project_key",
          "value": "<<selected_project>>"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "03e04301b15a7969",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Status classification"
    },
    {
      "id": "2b3357d90b70edb1",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Discover statuses",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "discover_statuses",
          "project_key": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.project_key>>"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e744f97eb579be2c",
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Statuses",
      "rows_formula": "<<STORY_RESULT('soc_data').discovered>>",
      "columns": [
        {
          "field": "status_name",
          "header": "Status"
        },
        {
          "field": "category_key",
          "header": "Category"
        },
        {
          "field": "suggested_classification",
          "header": "Suggested"
        },
        {
          "field": "_classify",
          "header": "Set to",
          "action_buttons": [
            {
              "label": "Queue",
              "trigger_story": "soc_data",
              "payload": {
                "action": "status_map_op",
                "op": "set",
                "key": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.project_key>>:<<row.status_name>>",
                "value": "queue"
              }
            },
            {
              "label": "Active",
              "trigger_story": "soc_data",
              "payload": {
                "action": "status_map_op",
                "op": "set",
                "key": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.project_key>>:<<row.status_name>>",
                "value": "active"
              }
            },
            {
              "label": "Done",
              "trigger_story": "soc_data",
              "payload": {
                "action": "status_map_op",
                "op": "set",
                "key": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.project_key>>:<<row.status_name>>",
                "value": "done"
              }
            },
            {
              "label": "Blocked",
              "trigger_story": "soc_data",
              "payload": {
                "action": "status_map_op",
                "op": "set",
                "key": "<<RESOURCE.soc_settings.project_key>>:<<row.status_name>>",
                "value": "blocked"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3dfae9d68590fef9",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Business hours"
    },
    {
      "id": "f38672fc0f5a142d",
      "type": "form",
      "title": "Business hours",
      "fields": [
        {
          "key": "start_hour",
          "type": "number",
          "label": "Start hour (0-23)"
        },
        {
          "key": "end_hour",
          "type": "number",
          "label": "End hour (0-23)"
        },
        {
          "key": "timezone",
          "type": "text",
          "label": "Timezone (IANA)"
        }
      ],
      "submit": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "settings_op",
          "op": "set",
          "key": "business_hours",
          "value": {
            "start_hour": "<<fields.start_hour>>",
            "end_hour": "<<fields.end_hour>>",
            "timezone": "<<fields.timezone>>",
            "work_days": [
              "Mon",
              "Tue",
              "Wed",
              "Thu",
              "Fri"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "df512b9cb3e7d8de",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Label filters"
    },
    {
      "id": "d3bea8363a5046e2",
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Labels",
      "rows_formula": "<<FLATTEN(MAP_LAMBDA(UNIQUE(FLATTEN(MAP_LAMBDA(RESOURCE.soc_tickets_cache.tickets, t, t.labels))), label, {\"label\": label, \"included\": RESOURCE.soc_label_config[label] | default(true)}))>>",
      "columns": [
        {
          "field": "label",
          "header": "Label"
        },
        {
          "field": "included",
          "header": "Included"
        },
        {
          "field": "_toggle",
          "header": "Toggle",
          "action_buttons": [
            {
              "label": "Include",
              "trigger_story": "soc_data",
              "payload": {
                "action": "labels_op",
                "op": "set",
                "key": "<<row.label>>",
                "value": true
              }
            },
            {
              "label": "Exclude",
              "trigger_story": "soc_data",
              "payload": {
                "action": "labels_op",
                "op": "set",
                "key": "<<row.label>>",
                "value": false
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "396f387f2e22fb29",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Sync controls"
    },
    {
      "id": "c69fe72dddb4b914",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Run sync now",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "sync_now"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ebea9452dff950c2",
      "type": "form",
      "title": "Sync interval (minutes)",
      "fields": [
        {
          "key": "sync_interval_minutes",
          "type": "number",
          "label": "Minutes"
        }
      ],
      "submit": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_data",
        "payload": {
          "action": "settings_op",
          "op": "set",
          "key": "sync_interval_minutes",
          "value": "<<fields.sync_interval_minutes>>"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "49f01a4751e1e0bf",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Reset"
    },
    {
      "id": "cff850f16499e786",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Reset settings (keep tickets)",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_reset",
        "payload": {
          "tier": "settings"
        },
        "confirm": "Reset settings?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c655c94ce843d593",
      "type": "button",
      "label": "Reset everything (keep credentials)",
      "action": {
        "trigger_story": "soc_reset",
        "payload": {
          "tier": "everything"
        },
        "confirm": "Reset all Resources? Credentials are NOT touched."
      }
    }
  ],
  "access": "tenant",
  "exported_at": "2026-04-21T00:00:00Z"
}